Privacy Policy

Offline Invoice Maker does not collect, transmit, sell, or share personal data.

All data entered in the app, including business profile details, clients, invoices, quotes, payment details, logos, backups, and generated PDF files, is stored locally on your device.

The app may access files or images only when you choose to import a backup, export a backup, select a logo, open a PDF, or share a PDF. These actions are initiated by you.

The app does not use analytics, advertising SDKs, tracking, accounts, or cloud storage.

If you delete data inside the app, it is removed from the app’s local storage. If you exported or shared files outside the app, you are responsible for managing those copies.

